        throw new Error('Browser ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ñ‡∏∂‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏•‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á');
      }
      
      const constraints = {
        video: { 
          width: { ideal: 640 }, 
          height: { ideal: 480 }, 
          facingMode: 'user'
